  "info": {
    "title": "Tasty API",
    "description": "## WebSocket Endpoints\n\n### Orders WebSocket\n`ws://{host}/ws/orders`\n\nReal-time order updates. Receives messages when orders are created, updated, or deleted.\n\n**Message format:**\n```json\n{ \"type\": \"created\" | \"updated\" | \"deleted\", \"order\": Order }\n```\n\n### Foods WebSocket\n`ws://{host}/ws/foods`\n\nReal-time food menu updates. Receives messages when food items are created, updated (including stock changes), or deleted.\n\n**Message format:**\n```json\n{ \"type\": \"created\" | \"updated\" | \"deleted\", \"food\": FoodItem }\n```",
    "version": "1.0.0"
  },
